        "IRS Publication 519 describes a dual-status tax year for non-citizens who are both a nonresident and a resident for federal tax purposes during the same year, which can apply to many arrival, departure, and adjustment-of-status fact patterns rather than interstate moves alone.": "IRS Publication 519 介绍了双重身份纳税年度,适用于在同一年度内对联邦税务而言既为非居民又为居民的非美国公民;该情形不仅限于州际搬屋,还可能出现于多种入境、离境与身份调整情形。",
        "IRS Publication 519 main page.": "IRS Publication 519 主页面。",
        "IRS Taxation of Dual-Status Individuals": "IRS《双重身份个人的税务》",
