        "IRS dual-status filer page. Final redirected URL uses the dual-status-individuals slug.": "IRS 双重身份申报者页面。最终重定向的 URL 使用 dual-status-individuals 路径。",
        "IRS general page on taxation of nonresident aliens.": "IRS 关于非居民外国人税务的概览页面。",
        "IRS guidance generally describes an exemption from FICA tax for wages paid for services performed by F-1, J-1, M-1, and Q nonresident-alien students, scholars, teachers, researchers, and trainees, when the work is part of the activity for which they were admitted and they remain nonresident aliens for federal tax purposes.": "IRS 指引通常说明,F-1、J-1、M-1 与 Q 非居民外国人学生、学者、教师、研究员及培训生因所从事工作而获得的工资,在该工作属于其被准予入境的活动一部分且其在联邦税务上仍为非居民外国人时,可享 FICA 税豁免。",
