        "If a credential is issued with an unexpected short term tied to a federal document, the timing of renewal can affect domestic flights, federal building access, and other tasks that may rely on a REAL ID after a move.": "若所核发证件因与联邦文件挂钩而出现意外的较短有效期,续证的时间安排可能影响国内航班、进入联邦建筑及搬屋后其他可能依赖 REAL ID 的事项。",
        "Illinois Board of Higher Education directory page on campus liaisons supporting students under state tuition-equity provisions.": "Illinois Board of Higher Education 关于在州学费公平条款下支持学生的校园联络员名录页面。",
        "Illinois Secretary of State Temporary Visitor Driver's License (TVDL) page. ilsos.gov returns a 302 redirect to its own page for curl HEAD requests, which is a known false negative on the long-standing .gov domain; the URL was confirmed via the Secretary of State's own search index.": "Illinois Secretary of State Temporary Visitor Driver's License(TVDL)页面。ilsos.gov 对 curl HEAD 请求返回 302 重定向至其自身页面,这是该长期存在的 .gov 域名上的已知误报;URL 已通过 Secretary of State 自身的检索索引予以确认。",
        "Illinois Student Assistance Commission resources page for non-U.S. citizen students including RISE Act and Alternative Application context. isac.org returns 403 to non-browser requests (anti-bot); this is a known false negative.": "Illinois Student Assistance Commission 面向非美国公民学生的资源页面,涵盖 RISE Act 与替代申请的背景信息。isac.org 对非浏览器请求返回 403(反机器人);属于已知误报。",
        "Immigration status - including Dreamer / DACA status - can significantly affect driver's licenses and REAL ID, professional licensure (especially nursing and healthcare), in-state tuition, SSN-related requirements, and state tax filing. Rules vary by state and federal law and change frequently.\n\nMoveSafe is not a substitute for legal counsel. Consider consulting a licensed immigration attorney before relying on any state-by-state summary.": "移民身份(包括 Dreamer / DACA 身份)可能对驾照与 REAL ID、专业执照(尤其是护理及医疗类)、本州学费、SSN 相关要求以及州税申报产生重大影响。各州规则及联邦法律不同,且经常变化。\n\nMoveSafe 不能替代法律咨询。在依据任何分州摘要作出决定前,请考虑咨询持证移民律师。",
        "Immunization requirements": "免疫接种要求",
        "Important to verify": "重要核实事项",
        "Information for Non-US Citizens": "非美国公民信息",
        "Inspection requirement": "检验要求",
        "Insurance networks, Medicaid and marketplace rules, and prescription transfer processes vary by state.": "保险网络、Medicaid 与医保市场规则,以及处方转移流程因州而异。",
        "Insurance networks, student health, prescriptions, primary care access.": "保险网络、学生医疗、处方药及基础医疗服务。",
        "Internship": "实习",
        "J-1 specific. Frame as verify with the program sponsor and reference 22 CFR Part 62. Do not state that any specific category does or does not require sponsor pre-approval for a particular change. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "仅适用于 J-1。请表述为需向项目主办方核实并参考 22 CFR Part 62。请勿陈述任何具体类别在某项变更上是否需要主办方事先批准。请避免使用 iOS SafeCopy 回避词表中的措辞。",
        "Jurisdiction: %@": "司法管辖类型:%@",
        "Know how to respond if asked to register to vote at the DMV": "了解在 DMV 被询问选民登记时如何回应",
        "L-1 and O-1 specific. Frame as verify against the approved petition and consult petitioner counsel. Do not state that an amendment is or is not needed for any specific scenario. Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list.": "仅适用于 L-1 与 O-1。请表述为需对照已批准申请核实并咨询申请人法律顾问。请勿就任何具体情景陈述是否需要修正申请。请避免使用 iOS SafeCopy 回避词表中的措辞。",
        "Language": "语言",
        "Last verified:": "上次核实:",
        "Last verified: %@": "上次核实:%@",
        "Lawful permanent residents (LPRs / green card holders) can face state-by-state variation in driver's license documents and REAL ID, professional licensure (especially nursing - foreign credentials evaluation may apply), Medicaid and state-marketplace eligibility (the federal 5-year bar interacts with state programs), state tax filing, and how DMVs handle voter-registration prompts (LPRs are not eligible to vote in federal or most state elections).\n\nMoveSafe is not a substitute for legal counsel. Consider consulting a licensed immigration attorney for status-affecting questions and a qualified tax professional for cross-state filing.": "合法永久居民(LPR / 绿卡持有人)在以下方面可能因州而异:驾照证件与 REAL ID、专业执照(尤其是护理-可能涉及外国学历认证)、Medicaid 与州医保市场资格(联邦五年等待期与州项目相互影响)、州税申报,以及 DMV 处理选民登记提示的方式(LPR 无资格在联邦及多数州的选举中投票)。\n\nMoveSafe 不能替代法律咨询。涉及身份的问题建议咨询持证移民律师,跨州税务申报建议咨询合格税务专业人士。",
        "Lease decisions made based on origin-state assumptions may not match destination-state rules.": "基于出发州假设作出的租约决定可能与目的地州规则不一致。",
        "Lease terms, security deposits, notice periods, and tenant protections.": "租约条款、押金、通知期及租客保护。",
        "Legal aid (general info)": "法律援助(一般信息)",
        "License transfer, deadlines, documents, and REAL ID awareness.": "驾照转换、办理期限、所需文件及 REAL ID 相关信息。",
        "Licensure requirements can affect clinical placement, NCLEX eligibility, endorsement, and employment timing.": "执照要求可能影响临床实习安排、NCLEX 资格、背书及就业时间。",
        "Links to official state agency sources": "链接到州政府官方机构来源",
        "Load example": "加载示例",
        "Local city/county rules may add protections. Review lease language directly.": "市 / 县级地方规则可能增加额外保护。请直接查阅租约条款。",
        "Local ordinance": "地方条例",
        "Local pet licensing requirements": "当地宠物登记要求",
        "Main USCIS page for H-1B specialty occupations classification.": "USCIS 关于 H-1B 专业职业类别的主页面。",
        "Many nonimmigrant visa holders are not within the standard Medicare or Medicaid eligibility groups, and federal rules in this area have been changing. Destination-state Medicaid rules add another layer that may differ from origin-state rules.": "许多非移民签证持有人不属于标准的 Medicare 或 Medicaid 资格群体,该领域的联邦规则曾发生变化。目的地州的 Medicaid 规则又增加一层,可能与出发州的规则不同。",
        "Many states require new residents to obtain a state driver's license within a specific period after becoming a resident.": "许多州要求新居民在成为居民后的指定期限内取得本州驾照。",
        "Mark as not verified": "标记为未核实",
        "Mark as verified": "标记为已核实",
        "Massachusetts Department of Revenue guide on personal income tax for nonresidents using Form 1-NR/PY. mass.gov returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative.": "Massachusetts Department of Revenue 关于非居民使用 Form 1-NR/PY 申报个人所得税的指南。mass.gov 对非浏览器请求返回 403(Cloudflare);属于已知误报。",
        "Massachusetts Department of Revenue guide on personal income tax for part-year residents. mass.gov returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative.": "Massachusetts Department of Revenue 关于部分年度居民申报个人所得税的指南。mass.gov 对非浏览器请求返回 403(Cloudflare);属于已知误报。",
        "Massachusetts RMV identification requirements page covering REAL ID, standard licenses, and lawful presence documentation. mass.gov returns 403 to non-browser requests (Cloudflare); this is a known false negative on the long-standing .gov-hosted state portal.": "Massachusetts RMV 身份证明要求页面,涵盖 REAL ID、标准驾照及合法居留文件。mass.gov 对非浏览器请求返回 403(Cloudflare);这是该长期存在的 .gov 托管州门户上的已知误报。",
        "Massachusetts identification (ID) requirements": "Massachusetts 身份证明(ID)要求",
        "May involve penalties or licensing consequences.": "可能涉及罚款或者执照方面个后果。",
        "Medicare.gov Get Started with Medicare": "Medicare.gov《开始了解 Medicare》",
        "Minimum coverage, state-specific rules, and policy address updates.": "最低保额、各州专属规则及保单地址更新。",
        "Missing a school or hospital onboarding requirement can delay clinical hours and graduation timing.": "未满足学校或医院的入科衔接要求可能延误临床学时及毕业时间。",
        "Missing a state motor vehicle deadline can create administrative or driving-related problems after relocation.": "错过州车管期限可能导致搬屋后出现行政或驾驶相关问题。",
        "Missing source": "缺失来源",
        "Missing the transfer reporting steps at the new school, or letting the transfer release date and program start fall out of sync, can affect status maintenance and access to on-campus work.": "未在新学校完成转移报到步骤,或转移释放日期与项目开始时间脱节,可能影响身份维持及校内工作的资格。",
        "Mixed jurisdiction": "混合司法管辖",
        "MoveSafe checklist": "MoveSafe 清单",
        "MoveSafe is a source-first checklist tool. It links you to official resources and highlights topics to verify. It does not provide legal advice.": "MoveSafe 是一款以来源为先个清单工具。它把你连到官方资源,点出要核实个主题。它不提供法律建议。",
        "MoveSafe is designed for state-to-state moves. You can still build a checklist, but some items may not apply.": "MoveSafe 是为跨州搬屋设计个。你还是可以生成清单,但有些项目可能不适用。",
        "MoveSafe prefers official agency sources. Placeholder entries should be replaced with verified URLs before production use.": "MoveSafe 优先用官方机构来源。占位项目应该在正式使用之前换成已核实个 URL。",
        "MoveSafe provides general legal and administrative information based on publicly available sources. It does not provide legal advice, does not create an attorney-client relationship, and should not be used as a substitute for advice from a licensed attorney in your jurisdiction. Laws and agency rules change frequently. Always verify information with official sources before making decisions.": "MoveSafe 基于公开可得的信息来源提供一般性法律及行政信息。本工具不提供法律建议、不构成律师-客户关系,且不应替代您所在司法管辖区持证律师的建议。法律与机构规则经常变化。请始终先向官方来源核实信息再作决定。",
        "Moving across state lines? Know what to verify before you go.": "要跨州搬屋啰?走之前晓得哪些事情要核实一下。",
        "Moving for school": "因为读书搬屋",
        "Moving for work": "因为工作搬屋",
        "Moving from %1$@ to %2$@": "从 %1$@ 搬到 %2$@",
        "Moving from one state's aid program to another's may change which aid applications to consider and which documents to gather, and this can affect how to plan tuition and living costs at the destination.": "从一州的助学项目转至另一州可能改变需要考虑的申请类型及所需准备的文件,这可能影响目的地学费与生活开销的规划。",
        "Moving may change which state tax withholding forms apply, and remote work can create cross-state payroll questions.": "搬屋可能改变适用的州税预扣表格,远程工作也可能引发跨州薪资问题。",
        "Moving to another state for clinical rotations, externships, or supervised practice.": "为临床轮转、院外实习或者督导下个实践而搬到另外一个州。",
        "NCLEX and license-by-endorsement steps can stall when documentation does not match a destination board's current rules, which can delay clinical placement, hire dates, and compact-state recognition.": "当文件不符合目的地委员会的现行规则时,NCLEX 与背书取得执照的流程可能停滞,进而延误临床实习安排、入职日期及 Compact 州的认可。",
        "NCLEX eligibility requirements": "NCLEX 资格要求",
        "NCSBN Licensure Compacts overview, including Nurse Licensure Compact context for non-citizen primary state of residency declarations.": "NCSBN 关于执照互认协议的概览,包括非美国公民主要居住州声明的 Nurse Licensure Compact 背景。",
        "National Council of State Boards of Nursing licensure guidance page for background context across boards.": "National Council of State Boards of Nursing 执照指引页面,提供各委员会的背景信息。",
        "New Jersey Office of the Secretary of Higher Education page summarizing the Tuition Equality Act and the 2020 statute affecting dependent students of H-1B holders.": "New Jersey Office of the Secretary of Higher Education 关于 Tuition Equality Act 及 2020 年影响 H-1B 持有人受抚养学生的法规的概览页面。",
        "New York DMV REAL ID page noting that an Enhanced ID is for U.S. citizens only and that REAL ID issued to applicants with temporary lawful status may expire with the federal document.": "New York DMV REAL ID 页面,指出 Enhanced ID 仅供美国公民使用,且向具有临时合法身份申请人核发的 REAL ID 可能随联邦文件一并到期。",
        "New York DMV documentation guidance for non-U.S. citizen applicants, including REAL ID and standard credentials.": "New York DMV 关于非美国公民申请人文件的指引,涵盖 REAL ID 与标准证件。",
        "New York Department of Taxation and Finance FAQ on residency, nonresident filing, and telecommuting.": "New York Department of Taxation and Finance 关于居住身份、非居民申报与远程办公的 FAQ。",
        "New York Department of Taxation and Finance page on nonresident and part-year filing using Form IT-203.": "New York Department of Taxation and Finance 关于使用 Form IT-203 进行非居民与部分年度申报的页面。",
        "New York State Education Department Office of the Professions RN licensure requirements page, which administers nursing licensure for New York.": "New York State Education Department Office of the Professions RN 执照要求页面,该机构负责 New York 的护理执照管理。",
        "No items match your filters": "冇得符合筛选条件个项目",
        "No source has been added yet for this item. Add an official source before relying on it.": "本项尚未添加来源。在依据本项之前,请先添加官方来源。",
        "No sources are attached to the items in this view.": "当前视图中个项目还冇得任何来源。",
        "Nonimmigrant visa holders (F-1, H-1B, J-1, L-1, O-1, and others) face state-by-state variation in driver's license documents and REAL ID (often tied to I-94 / visa dates), in-state tuition (most public universities classify F-1 students as out-of-state), professional licensure documentation, tax residency rules, and health-insurance options. USCIS also requires reporting any address change within 10 days via Form AR-11.\n\nMoveSafe is not a substitute for legal counsel. Consider consulting a licensed immigration attorney, your school's DSO if on F-1, employer HR or immigration counsel if on a work visa, and a qualified tax professional for cross-state filing.": "非移民签证持有人(F-1、H-1B、J-1、L-1、O-1 及其他)在以下方面可能因州而异:驾照证件与 REAL ID(通常与 I-94 / 签证日期挂钩)、本州学费(多数公立大学将 F-1 学生归类为外州学生)、专业执照所需文件、税务居住身份规则,以及医疗保险选项。USCIS 还要求在地址变更后 10 天内通过 Form AR-11 进行申报。\n\nMoveSafe 不能替代法律咨询。建议咨询持证移民律师;若持 F-1 签证,请联系学校的 DSO;若持工作签证,请联系雇主人力资源或移民法律顾问;跨州税务申报请咨询合格税务专业人士。",
        "Nonresident and part-year resident forms and instructions": "非居民与部分年度居民表格及说明",
