        "Texas Department of Public Safety driver license identification documentation page covering U.S. citizen and non-U.S. citizen applicants.": "Texas Department of Public Safety 关于驾照身份证明文件的页面,涉及美国公民与非美国公民申请人。",
        "Texas Higher Education Coordinating Board page on residency for tuition purposes, including categories of nonimmigrant applicants and special pathways under the Texas Education Code.": "Texas Higher Education Coordinating Board 关于学费居住身份的页面,包括非移民申请人类别及 Texas Education Code 下的特别途径。",
