        "This checklist is not a legal conclusion. Verify with official sources and consult a licensed professional where appropriate.": "此清单不是法律结论。请向官方来源核实,并在合适情况下咨询持证专业人士。",
        "This source has not been verified in more than a year. Treat as stale and verify directly with the official source.": "此来源已超过一年未核实。请视为过时来源,并直接向官方来源核实。",
        "This source has not been verified in more than six months. Check the official website before relying on it.": "此来源已超过六个月未核实。在依据此来源前,请检查官方网站。",
