        "Title transfer process": "产权转移流程",
        "Total topics to verify: %d": "要核实个主题拢共:%d",
        "Travel documentation if flying with a pet": "携带宠物搭机所需的旅行文件",
        "Treating an intra-MSA worksite change as a full new petition can create unnecessary cost and timing risk, while assuming portability rules apply without checking the MSA boundaries can lead to status questions later.": "将 MSA 内的工作地点变更当作全新申请来处理,可能带来不必要的成本与时间风险;而未确认 MSA 边界即假设流动性规则适用,日后可能引发身份问题。",
        "Treats high-risk categories with a \"Do not assume\" label": "对高风险类别打上「莫假设」标签",
        "Try clearing risk filters or the high-risk / stale-source toggles.": "请试一下清除风险筛选,或者关掉「高风险」/「过时来源」开关。",
        "USCIS AR-11 Alien's Change of Address Card": "USCIS AR-11 外籍人士地址变更卡",
        "USCIS Employment Authorization page providing background on the EAD (Form I-766) used in some state DMV and licensing document lists.": "USCIS《工作授权》页面,提供关于 EAD(Form I-766)的背景信息,该证件出现在部分州 DMV 与执照文件清单中。",
        "USCIS Final Guidance on When to File an Amended or New H-1B Petition After Matter of Simeio Solutions LLC": "USCIS《Matter of Simeio Solutions LLC 之后何时提交 H-1B 修正或新申请的最终指引》",
        "USCIS H-1B Specialty Occupations Landing Page": "USCIS H-1B Specialty Occupations 入口页面",
