        "USCIS O-1 classification page.": "USCIS O-1 类别页面。",
        "USCIS Policy Manual Volume 1 Part A Chapter 10 Changes of Address": "USCIS Policy Manual 第一卷 A 部分第 10 章《地址变更》",
        "USCIS Policy Manual chapter that describes federal address-change reporting.": "USCIS Policy Manual 中介绍联邦地址变更申报的章节。",
        "USCIS archive page summarizing the 2015 Simeio Solutions final guidance and the LCA-amendment trigger for worksite changes outside the MSA.": "USCIS 存档页面,概述 2015 年 Simeio Solutions 最终指引及在 MSA 之外变更工作地点触发 LCA 修正的要求。",
        "USCIS guidance generally indicates that a U.S. Postal Service change-of-address request does not change a record with USCIS and that USPS does not forward USCIS mail. A destination-state DMV address update is also a separate step from the federal AR-11 filing.": "USCIS 指引通常表明,USPS 地址变更请求不会更改 USCIS 的记录,且 USPS 不会转寄 USCIS 邮件。目的地州 DMV 地址更新也与联邦 AR-11 申报属于独立步骤。",
        "USCIS guidance generally indicates that an H-1B worker moving to a new worksite within the same MSA or area of intended employment as the existing LCA does not require a new LCA or an amended H-1B petition, although the existing LCA may still need to be posted at the new worksite. The federal AR-11 address change requirement still applies to the worker.": "USCIS 指引通常表明,H-1B 雇员在现行 LCA 所属同一 MSA 或预期就业地区内搬屋至新工作地点时,不需新的 LCA 或修正后的 H-1B 申请,但现行 LCA 可能仍需在新工作地点张贴。联邦 AR-11 地址变更要求对该雇员仍然适用。",
        "USCIS newsroom alert describing the online change-of-address tool and clarifying that USPS forwarding does not change a USCIS record.": "USCIS 新闻室公告,介绍在线地址变更工具,并澄清 USPS 转寄不会更改 USCIS 记录。",
        "USCIS umbrella page on the federal change-of-address requirement, including the online change-of-address tool.": "USCIS 关于联邦地址变更要求的综合页面,包含在线地址变更工具。",
        "USPS Mail Forwarding / Change of Address": "USPS 邮件转寄 / 地址变更",
        "USPS mail-forwarding page; referenced to clarify that USPS change-of-address does not substitute for federal AR-11 filing per USCIS guidance.": "USPS 邮件转寄页面;此处引用是为了根据 USCIS 指引澄清,USPS 地址变更不能替代联邦 AR-11 申报。",
        "Under 22 CFR Part 62, J-1 program sponsors maintain the SEVIS record and monitor the site of activity for each exchange visitor. A move that changes residence, site of activity, or host organization generally triggers an exchange-visitor reporting obligation to the sponsor and a sponsor update to SEVIS.": "根据 22 CFR Part 62,J-1 项目主办方负责维护 SEVIS 记录,并监督每位交流访客的活动地点。涉及居所、活动地点或接待机构变更的搬屋,通常触发交流访客向主办方的报告义务,以及主办方对 SEVIS 的更新。",
        "Under USCIS guidance following Matter of Simeio Solutions (2015), an H-1B worker's move to a worksite outside the metropolitan statistical area (MSA) or area of intended employment listed on the current Labor Condition Application (LCA) is generally a material change that calls for a new LCA and an amended H-1B petition.": "依据 USCIS 在 Matter of Simeio Solutions(2015)之后发布的指引,H-1B 雇员搬屋至现行 Labor Condition Application(LCA)所列大都会统计区(MSA)或预期就业地区之外的工作地点,通常构成重大变更,需要提交新的 LCA 及修正后的 H-1B 申请。",
        "Understand how the destination state defines residency": "了解目的地州对居住身份的定义",
        "University of California admissions page on the AB 540 nonresident tuition exemption, noting that most nonimmigrant visa holders such as F-1 or J-1 generally cannot establish California residency for tuition purposes.": "University of California 招生页面关于 AB 540 非居民学费豁免的说明,指出多数非移民签证持有人(如 F-1 或 J-1)通常无法在学费上确立 California 居住身份。",
        "Update employment paperwork and state tax forms": "更新就业文件及州税表",
        "Use do not assume language. Do not state that USPS or DMV updates can substitute for AR-11 (USCIS guidance says they generally do not). Avoid the iOS SafeCopy avoid-list (legal-conclusion phrasing and penalty-avoidance phrasing).": "请使用「莫假设」措辞。请勿陈述 USPS 或 DMV 的更新可代替 AR-11(USCIS 指引通常表明不可)。请避免使用 iOS SafeCopy 回避词表中的法律结论性措辞及规避处罚类措辞。",
        "Vaccination, licensing, breed restrictions, housing pet policies.": "疫苗接种、登记、品种限制及住房宠物政策。",
        "Vaccination, local licensing, breed restrictions, and landlord pet policies can vary across destination states and cities.": "疫苗接种、地方登记、品种限制及房东宠物政策可能因目的地州和城市不同而有所差异。",
        "Vehicle registration": "车辆登记",
        "Vehicle registration rules can change after a state-to-state move, especially if the destination state treats you as a new resident.": "跨州搬屋后,车辆登记规则可能发生变化,尤其当目的地州将您视为新居民时。",
